70180051;TV Show;H2O: Just Add Water;;Cariba Heine, Phoebe Tonkin, Angus McLaren, Burgess Abernethy, Claire Holt, Alan David Lee, Cleo Massey, Jamie Timony;Australia; February 8, 2017;2009;TV-PG;3 Seasons;Kids' TV, TV Dramas;The gals in this fantasy series cope with the burden of growing a giant fin and transforming into mermaids whenever they come in contact with water.